title: Fill In The Gap (Larry Brey)
description: Are you letting disappointment disrupt your destiny? In “Fill In The Gap,” Elevation Church’s Associate Pastor, Larry Brey, reveals how when we’re facing disappointment, we can either embrace God’s blessings or turn to our own bitterness.
